---
title: Tomato-Garlic Beef Ragu with Courgette, Spaghetti and Italian Cheese
description: Long day? Too tired to cook? We know the feeling. At HelloFresh we believe that being short of time or stuck in a recipe rut shouldn’t stop you from cooking and enjoying great food. Packed with fresh, delicious flavours and good-for you ingredients, our speedy beef ragu is about to become your favourite quick-fix recipe. When you can get full on flavour in double quick time, you know you’re onto a winner. Enjoy!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/tomato-garlic-beeg-ragu-29f5fadd.jpg
